programs.title: Internships
programs.content: Students who passed their interviews get 3-month internships to gain experience in building scalable products that are widely used around the world.

programs.title: 360° Training
programs.content: A2SV upskills students with a 360° software engineering program that focuses on problem-solving, effective speaking, and personal development.

programs.title: Social Projects
programs.content: Students work on social projects with industry experts to address the most pressing problems in their community.
